stimulusHtml:
Answer all parts of the question that follows.

a) Identify ONE continuity in the political systems of South or Southeast Asia in the period 1750–1900.

b) Identify ONE change in the political systems of South or Southeast Asia in the period 1750–1900.

c) Explain ONE way in which changes in the global economy led to changes in the political systems of South or Southeast Asia in the period 1750–1900.
